about: I began my career working with Software Testing, my first job within the IT industry. This opportunity opened the door to my beginning at IBM where I worked with Oracle Database development and analysis, in this case specifically my first contact with coding and a feeling that varies between discoveries, learning, frustration, expectation and hours of hard work in solving errors. Despite the hard work invested in addressing these challenges, the satisfaction derived from resolving problems and meeting expectations cannot be overlooked. I believe every Developer identifies with these moments in their career, forming a deep passion for what we do.An informal conversation with a childhood friend, who happens to be an excellent Developer, sparked my interest in Web development. This led me to enroll in a bootcamp, an experience that felt like love at first sight! Over the years, my journey in Web development has continued, with a daily commitment to progress and staying updated on the latest technologies in the market.In summary, I am a Software Developer/Analyst with a successful 8+ years of experience.Please refer to my resume for details of my previous experience and skill set.Interested in checking the code I have worked? Please access my GitHub Profile:https://github.com/fsalviatihttps://salviati-portfolio.vercel.app/

His willingness to step outside his comfort zone and tackle complex projects showcases his potential for growth.

I highly recommend Fernando to any team seeking a talented and motivated developer.‚Äù

recommendations.name: Anushka Jayasekara
recommendations.summary:
‚ÄúI had the privilege of working with Fernando on the same team, and I can confidently say that he is an exceptional Full Stack Developer and a true asset to any team. His ability to collaborate seamlessly with team members and communicate complex ideas in an accessible manner truly stands out.

Fernando's technical skills are outstanding, spanning both front-end and back-end development. He consistently delivers high-quality code that is efficient and reliable. Whether it's tackling challenging tasks or refining intricate details, his dedication to excellence is evident in every aspect of his work.

What sets Fernando apart is not only his technical expertise but also his efficiency and ability to meet tight deadlines without compromising the quality of the final product. He approaches each challenge with a solution-oriented and positive mindset, making him an indispensable team player.

I highly recommend having Fernando on any team. His skills, professionalism, and collaborative spirit will undoubtedly elevate any project he is part of.‚Äù
